<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cookie Policy — Shurget</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Shurget Cookie Policy — what cookies we use and how to control them.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/theme.css">
  <style>
    body { background: var(--bg); }
    .legal-page {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 100px 1.5rem 5rem;
    }
    .legal-nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .legal-nav a {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--gray-mid);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .legal-nav a:hover { color: var(--orange); }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .page-meta {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--gray-mid);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    h2:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; border-top: none; }
    p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--gray-mid); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    li { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--gray-mid); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    li strong { color: var(--charcoal); }
    .cookie-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }
    .cookie-table th {
      background: var(--off-white);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .cookie-table td {
      padding: 0.65rem 0.9rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      color: var(--gray-mid);
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    .cookie-table td:first-child { font-weight: 600; color: var(--charcoal); white-space: nowrap; }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.15rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .badge-required { background: #fff0e6; color: #c44e03; }
    .badge-optional { background: #e8f5e9; color: #2e7d32; }
    .summary-box {
      background: var(--off-white);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--orange);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .summary-box p { margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .footer-legal {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 4rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .footer-legal a { color: var(--orange); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .footer-legal a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .manage-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem;
      background: var(--charcoal);
      color: var(--white);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .manage-btn:hover { background: #444; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="legal-page">
    <nav class="legal-nav" aria-label="Legal navigation">
      <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/cookies" style="color:var(--orange);">Cookie Policy</a>
    </nav>

    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="page-meta">Last updated: June 18, 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Effective immediately</p>

    <div class="summary-box">
      <p><strong>We use a minimal set of cookies.</strong> Essential cookies keep the site working. Analytics cookies (GA4) fire only after you consent. We do not use advertising cookies or sell your data to any third party.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>What is a Cookie?</h2>
    <p>A cookie is a small text file stored in your browser when you visit a website. Cookies help sites remember preferences, keep you logged in, and understand how visitors use the site.</p>

    <h2>Cookies We Use</h2>
    <table class="cookie-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Cookie</th>
          <th>Source</th>
          <th>Purpose</th>
          <th>Duration</th>
          <th>Type</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>haulr_consent</td>
          <td>Shurget</td>
          <td>Stores your cookie consent choice (accepted or declined) so we don't ask every visit.</td>
          <td>12 months</td>
          <td><span class="badge badge-required">Essential</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>haulr_admin</td>
          <td>Shurget</td>
          <td>Signed session cookie for admin authentication. Only set when an admin logs in. Never set for regular users.</td>
          <td>8 hours</td>
          <td><span class="badge badge-required">Essential</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>_ga, _ga_*</td>
          <td>Google Analytics 4</td>
          <td>Tracks anonymous page views, session counts, traffic sources, and booking-funnel events so we can understand how the site is used and improve it. No personally identifiable information is included.</td>
          <td>Up to 2 years</td>
          <td><span class="badge badge-optional">Analytics (consent required)</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Stripe cookies</td>
          <td>Stripe</td>
          <td>Stripe sets its own cookies during the checkout process to handle payment fraud detection and session continuity. These are only active on Stripe-hosted checkout pages. See <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Stripe's privacy policy</a>.</td>
          <td>Varies</td>
          <td><span class="badge badge-required">Essential (third-party)</span></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Analytics Cookies in Detail</h2>
    <p>We use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to understand how visitors use shurget.com — which pages are most popular, where traffic comes from, and how people move through the booking flow. GA4 uses anonymous identifiers; it does not receive your name, email, or payment information.</p>
    <p>GA4 only fires after you click <strong>Accept all</strong> on the cookie banner. If you click <strong>Essential only</strong>, the GA4 script is not initialized and no data is sent to Google.</p>

    <h2>No Advertising Cookies</h2>
    <p>Shurget does not run retargeting ads, use Facebook Pixel, or any advertising network cookies. We do not build advertising profiles from your browsing behavior.</p>

    <h2>Managing Your Cookie Preferences</h2>
    <p>You can change your preference at any time. When you click the button below, the preference stored in your browser is cleared and the consent banner reappears on your next page load.</p>
    <button class="manage-btn" id="reset-consent-btn">Reset Cookie Preferences</button>

    <p style="margin-top:1.25rem;">You can also disable cookies entirely in your browser settings, though this may affect site functionality (login sessions, for example).</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about cookies or data? Email <a href="mailto:support@shurget.com">support@shurget.com</a> or see our full <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <div class="footer-legal">
      <a href="/">← Back to Shurget</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
  document.getElementById('reset-consent-btn').addEventListener('click', function () {
    // Clear from localStorage (new consent mechanism)
    localStorage.removeItem('haulr_consent');
    localStorage.removeItem('haulr_consent_ts');
    // Also clear legacy cookie if present
    document.cookie = 'haulr_consent=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 UTC; path=/; SameSite=Lax';
    document.documentElement.removeAttribute('data-cc-granted');
    document.documentElement.removeAttribute('data-cc-analytics');
    alert('Cookie preferences cleared. The banner will reappear on your next page visit.');
  });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
